  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "I noticed in the most recent version (v4.9.0) that it is now necessary to explicitly specify the contract owner as a constructor argument, rather than having the owner automatically set.\r\n\r\nI also saw that the statement \"By default, the owner account will be the one that deploys the contract\" is no longer accurate.\r\n\r\nI suggest it should now say, \"The owner account is provided as a constructor argument during deployment.\" ",
